{"tid":2097990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友女友係PTGF，你問我代朋友答！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2020-07-07T07:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T00:38:59.000Z","uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcce2f7efa73fd1b15201120f9f214d8f0a653b0","tid":2097990,"uid":56875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\">追咗好耐，由朋友聚會到相約獨處。感情一路發展得好平穩，好正常。<br />\n但發覺對方身邊朋友比較多。出街時，機不離手。忙著覆wechat，whataspp，睇FB，睇IG等等。仲意為自己女友係分分鐘幾百萬上落添。咁多嘢要txt? 忙麼?!<br />\n有時whatsapp佢又唔覆，又冇離線時間，又睇唔到雙藍click。好想知佢做緊乜，但又永遠突然好似人間蒸發咁。搵極都唔覆機。唔知意為無自己電話壞咗添。<br />\n有一晚，喺IG search search 下，發覺有個女仔好似佢。咪嚐試下用其他IG加佢啦，傾傾下，我好有衝動約佢，睇下係咪自己心入邊嘅答案啦。點知出到黎原來真係自己女朋友! 真係book佢個街des! 成個人呆咗。有如自己失足，跪喺個鬧市中心，眼佈紅根半反白眼，口也半開不合，天旋地轉。世界變得不再真實。<br />\n當然，個陣我唔敢行埋去啦。諗咗好耐好耐，究竟，應唔應該繼續同一個咁嘅女仔一齊好呢? 定係飛咗佢? 再搵過個好嘅? 但現在好多呢啲女仔，唔覺意又中彩又點呢?</div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://go.discuss.com.hk/?id=58941X1369525&amp;isjs=1&amp;jv=14.1.5-stackpath&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fladies.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Fpage%3D1%26tid%3D28045625&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fede5cd%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_190220%2F20190220_db3d36dbc47f3a996410tJXKdUONAY2J.jpg&amp;xguid=b0882e2567da917275d0f64cfeabfc01&amp;xs=1&amp;xtz=-480&amp;xuuid=e5c0ce54824e2dffbfb2c334967cb844&amp;xjsf=other_click__auxclick%20%5B2%5D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgo.discuss.com.hk%2F%3Fid%3D58941X1369525%26isjs%3D1%26jv%3D14.1.5-stackpath%26sref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fladies.discuss.com.hk%252Fviewthread.php%253Fpage%253D1%2526tid%253D28045625%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%252Ft%252Fede5cd%252Ff%252F800x0%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fimg.discuss.com.hk%252Fd%252Fattachments%252Fday_190220%252F20190220_db3d36dbc47f3a996410tJXKdUONAY2J.jpg%26xguid%3Db0882e2567da917275d0f64cfeabfc01%26xs%3D1%26xtz%3D-48